						In Class Exercise - 1 + 2

No.1 : Write a Python program which takes positive numbers as input and print their sum until an odd number is given(as input).




No.2 : Write a Python program to find a factorial of a number. // 0 = 1, 1! = 1, 2! = 2, 3! = 6, 4! = 24, n! = 1 x....n




No.3 : Write a Python program to check if the input character is a vowel or a consonant. 




No.4 : Write a Python program to check if the input integer is a prime number or not.